    "zh": "线控制动与制动分配",
    "en": "Brake-by-wire and brake bias"
  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "混合动力时代 F1 用线控制动把后轴机械制动与 MGU-K 能量回收无缝叠加，并由电控实时分配前后制动力，以稳定车手脚下那块被电机「吃掉」的制动踏板感。",
    "en": "In the hybrid era F1 uses brake-by-wire to blend rear-axle mechanical braking with MGU-K energy recovery, electronically splitting front/rear bias to stabilise the pedal feel the motor 'steals'."
  },
